Class NumberType<T extends Number>

java.lang.Object
  se.softhouse.common.numbers.NumberType<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the subclass of Number
public abstract class NumberType<T extends Number>
extends Object

A class that exposes static fields (and functions), such as Integer.MAX_VALUE and Integer.decode(String), for subclasses of Number in an object oriented way
